@startuml
!include ../includes/appsec-style.puml
title AppSec Process 04: SCA & Dependency Vulnerability Management (GHAS + Trivy)

' Purpose: Control open-source risk (vulns + licenses) with AppCode-based ownership and automation.

start

partition "Discover" {
  :Detect dependencies (manifests/lockfiles);
  :Generate/update SBOM (Trivy) (AppCode);
}

partition "Scan" {
  :GHAS dependency review (PR);
  :Dependabot alerts (default);
  :License policy checks;
}

partition "Triage" {
  :Normalize findings (CVE/CWE/license);
  :Correlate to AppCode + repo owner;
  if (Critical/high?) then (Yes)
    :Block merge / release as needed<<gate>>;
  else (No)
    :Queue in backlog;
  endif
}

partition "Remediate" {
  :Auto-PR (Dependabot) or manual upgrade;
  :Test + rebuild;
}

partition "Verify & Close" {
  :Re-scan on PR + main;
  :Close ticket / alert;
  :Report MTTR by AppCode;
}

note right
Key message: **Dependencies are code** — manage with the same gates and SLAs.
end note

stop
@enduml
